Description:
    Bootstraps Rails Hyperdrive in this app:
      - writes .mcp.json (Claude Code config)
      - writes CLAUDE.md (top-level instructions, references skills + StackProfile)
      - installs selected architecture skills into .claude/skills/
      - discovers and installs 3rd-party gem-shipped skills (with audit headers)
      - mounts Rails::Hyperdrive::Engine at /_hyperdrive in config/routes.rb (idempotent)

Examples:
    bin/rails hyperdrive:init
    bin/rails hyperdrive:init --yes
    bin/rails hyperdrive:init --mount-at /admin/hyperdrive
    bin/rails hyperdrive:init --skip-skills
    bin/rails hyperdrive:init --dry-run
